OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTalking therapies may help 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmenopause mood - study     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Mindfulness, group and cognitive       
OL,6, behavioural therapy could effectively  
OL,7, treat menopause symptoms such as low   
OL,8, mood and anxiety, analysis suggests.   
OL,10,FThe University College London research,
OL,11,Fpublished in the Journal of Affective  
OL,12,FDisorders, examined 30 studies         
OL,13,Finvolving 3,500 women in 14 countries, 
OL,14,Fincluding the UK, the US and Australia.
OL,16,FDraft NHS guidelines recommend offering
OL,17,FCBT alongside or instead of HRT.       
OL,19,FIt could "give GPs and patients more   
OL,20,Foptions", the researchers said.        
